CM_ SG_ 938 RESTransmissionStatus "Indicates whether the remote start precondition of transmission in Park was met. The value must not be relied upon outside the context of a remote engine start operation.";
CM_ SG_ 938 RESVehicleLockStatus "Indicates whether the remote start precondition of vehicle locked was met. The value must not be relied upon outside the context of a remote engine start operation.";
