CM_ SG_ 226 ImmoAuthPKeyMainReq "Passive Control Challenge

The MSB of the signal must be written to the COM layer first (with an offset of zero in wr_bytes() ) and therefore transmitted on the bus first.
Similarly, subscribing modules will receive the MSB of the signal when they call rd_bytes(0).

E.g. wr_bytes(0) = published_signal_MSB;

Subscribed_Signal_MSB = rd_bytes(0);
";
CM_ SG_ 227 CLockCmd_2 "Central Locking command to control the latch actuators.

Bitcoded:
CentralLock                   0000 0001
CentralUnlock                0000 0010
CentralDL                       0000 0011
CentralUnlockDL           0000 0100
TrunkLock                     0000 0101
TrunkUnlock                  0000 0110
DDUnlock                      xxx1 1111
PDUnlock                      xx1x 1111
LRUnlock                      x1xx 1111
RRUnlock                      1xxx 1111
DDLock                         xxx1 0000
PDLock                         xx1x 0000
LRLock                         x1xx 0000
RRLock                         1xxx 0000
CrashUnlock                  0000 1000 ";
