CM_ SG_ 230 DirectionIndication "Description for X150 and X250
========================

Provides an output to the cluster (light indication) to show the direction indication mode selected by the user.
This sporadic signal is packed into a periodic frame.

Description for L322, L538 and T5
======================

This signal DirectionIndication signal is sent to DriverInformationMgr and rear view mirror on right and left side, when the DirectionIndication is activated. The DriverInformationMgr will inform the Driver/User by an indicator who will illuminate on the DriverIformationMgr. Observation (the indicator will illuminate when DirectionIndication are activated in mode Left, Right and Hazard).
";
