CM_ SG_ 414 KVDecryptedMsg2 "Remote decrypted command from KVM.
Previously unused value 1101 now to be used.
Meaning for this value :- Return suspension to normal height.
No changes to any other signal definitions or parameters.

Bit 4 Button Status: 0 = Not held, 1 = Button Held (Jaguar documentation only)
";
CM_ SG_ 414 PECentralLockCmd2 "Passive Entry lock/unlock request
