CM_ SG_ 1025 CcfEMMaxDurEngOff "Signal required to transmit CCF variable EMMaxDurEngOff to the PCM. which allows the dealer to update the maximum time between engine maintenance engine starts. If we find that certain combinations of components in certain regions require shorter intervals, then this car config parameter will save us time and money.

