CM_ SG_ 1025 CcfFMMaxFuelAge "Signal required to transmit CCF variable FMMaxFuelAge to the PCM. Which allows the dealer to update the maximum fuel age before fuel maintanance mode starts. If we find that certain combinations of componants in certain reigions require shorter or longer intervals, then this car config perameter will save us time and money.
